      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54B32 high-pressure 3.2L inline-six. This engine remains a masterpiece of engineering, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and optimized by a fully serviced double VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring tactile engagement and predictable power delivery. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement, addressing the chassis' known harmonic stress points. While the exterior shows honest patina expected of a driver\u2019s car, the suspension kinematics remain tight, and the throttle response is razor-sharp. A purist-spec machine ready for the apex.",
